  m_text: '1. Pour water into Cup A.

    2. Add borax into Cup A.

    3. Stir Cup
    A with the popsicle stick.

    4. Pour water into Cup B.

    5. Add glue into
    Cup B.

    6. Stir Cup B with the popsicle stick.

    7. Pour the borax solution
    (Cup A) into Cup B.

    8. Stir the mixture with the popsicle stick.

    9.
    Remove the slime from Cup B.'
